overview: In this video Master Luke Chan demonstrates step-by-step instructions of the three basic practices of Chi-lel. It includes actual footage of cancer being dissolved through the sending of chi. It shows the Center in China, a medicineless hospital where there are no patients only students, there is no other form of treatment other than the practice of self healing and group healing through chi.
tagline: Chi-lel Qigong for Health, Longevity, Creativity, and Mental Clarity
title: 101 Miracles of Natural Healing
